comment_data.body: I think this change means we will not be able to launch Android Studio in the debugger. But I haven't been able to do that since late last year, due to a Kotlin compiler bug, so that's not a blocker. Anyway, if the bug gets fixed I can add some code to the `plugin` tool to fix up the `plugin.xml` content.
